name: FBoxSphereBounds3d
doc:
A bounding box and bounding sphere with the same origin.
@note The full C++ class is located here : Engine\Source\Runtime\Core\Public\Math\BoxSphereBounds.h

Origin: Holds the origin of the bounding box and sphere.
BoxExtent: Holds the extent of the bounding box, which is half the size of the box in 3D space
SphereRadius: Holds the radius of the bounding sphere.
